roken arm and had a major case of whiplash. I ended up getting back to school only an hour and a half late. When I got back to school I was cheered over the school loud speaker and congratulated by my friends. That was my good dead for the day. It was a very odd day for me. The operator said if I was 5 minutes later he might not have made it.<br>
<br>
